About this item
【earbuds for phone calls & good sound quality】ANC and ENC 2 mics noise reduction, answering the phone call will not be disturbed by external noise. Upgraded dynamic speaker provide good sound quality for the bluetooth headphones earbuds.
【Control with APP】The wireless earbuds provide free APP to control the sound effects, timed pause music play, etc. You could customize the touch control of the bluetooth earbuds on the APP.
【Wireless earbuds noise cancelling】The wireless earphones have three Noise Cancellation Modes. Press the bud for 1s to switch Mild noise cancelling, strong noise cancelling and transparency mode.
【Bluetooth 5.3】The latest Bluetooth versions offer one-step Pairing and works within 10 meters. Simple connection setup, When you take out the earbuds from the charging case, the Bluetooth headphone will connect to the last paired device automatically. The wireless ear buds compatible with iPhone, Android phone and iPad, etc.
【Water Resistance Wireless Earbuds】IPX5 waterproof technology, protect the Bluetooth earbuds from sweat and water splash. The sport earbuds mifo HiFiAir are suitable for running, workout.
【Small Size earbuds& Comfortable wearing】Weighing only 4.5g each bud. The small size and light of the wireless earbuds Provides a stable and comfortable wearing. The earbuds provide 30h play time including the charging case.